name: Intra-city-route-finder
body:
Intra-City-Route-Finder

Course: Artificial Intelligence Lab

Features

  • Contains map of a city using graph database
  • Finds shortest and fastest route from the traffic factor of a road and cost of transportation
  • Can show driving route to google map

Screenshots

Limitations

  • Could not implement the features correctly since i got only one day for making this project

Future plan

  • Addition of a fuzzy logic AI for choosing shortest traffic time and cheapest costs
  • Showing route on google map
